            Roman&quot;" lang="EN-GB">SI d'aide &agrave; la d&eacute;cision : <i
              style="mso-bidi-font-style:normal">BD
              multidimensionnelles, entrep&ocirc;ts de donn&eacute;es</i></span></li>
        <li><span
            style="font-family:Times;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times
            New Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language: FR">Gestion des donn&eacute;es
            massives dans les SI :<i style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal">
              tra&ccedil;abilit&eacute;, contextualisation, extraction, interpr&eacute;tation
              des informations <o:p></o:p></i></span></li>
        <li><small>S&eacute;curit&eacute; des syst&egrave;mes d&#8217;information; <i>s&eacute;curit&eacute;
              organisationnelle, s&eacute;curit&eacute; d&#8217;acc&egrave;s &agrave; l&#8217;information, prise
              en compte de la s&eacute;curit&eacute; d&egrave;s la conception, mod&egrave;les
              multi-politiques</i><o:p></o:p></small></li>
        <li><span
            style="font-family:Times;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times
            New Roman&quot;; mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New
            Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:FR">Syst&egrave;mes d&#8217;information
            h&eacute;t&eacute;rog&egrave;nes et distribu&eacute;s : <i>plateformes
              informationnelles, nouvelles architectures, m&eacute;diation de
              sources d&#8217;information (donn&eacute;es et connaissances)
              h&eacute;t&eacute;rog&egrave;nes, e-services, int&eacute;gration via les services,
              organisations virtuelles, travail collaboratif, cloud
              computing, big data</i><o:p></o:p></span></li>
        <li><span
            style="font-family:Times;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times
            New Roman&quot;; mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New
            Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:FR">Ing&eacute;nierie des syst&egrave;mes
            d&#8217;information dirig&eacute;e par les mod&egrave;les : <i>transformation,
              r&eacute;utilisation, &eacute;volution, gestion des mod&egrave;les,
              technologies de l&#8217;IDM, r&eacute;tro-ing&eacute;nierie et r&eacute;ing&eacute;nierie
              des SI</i><o:p></o:p></span></li>
        <li><span
            style="font-family:Times;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times
            New Roman&quot;; mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New
            Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:FR">Management et gouvernance
            des syst&egrave;mes d&#8217;information <i>: ing&eacute;nierie d'entreprise,
              gestion des risques, mesure, optimisation, &eacute;valuation,
              audit et qualit&eacute; des SI, reconfiguration des processus,
              gestion des syst&egrave;mes &laquo;&nbsp;l&eacute;gataires&nbsp;&raquo;, alignement des SI &agrave;
              la strat&eacute;gie d&#8217;entreprise</i><o:p></o:p></span></li>
        <li><span
            style="font-family:Times;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times
            New Roman&quot;; mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New
            Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:FR">Ing&eacute;nierie des documents
            et des connaissances :<i> mod&eacute;lisation et structuration des
              informations documentaires, recherche d'informations,
              recommandation d'informations, gestion &eacute;lectronique de
              documents et de contenu, m&eacute;tadonn&eacute;es, ontologies,
              classification de documents</i> <o:p></o:p></span></li>
        <li><span
            style="font-family:Times;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times
            New Roman&quot;; mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New
            Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:FR">Syst&egrave;mes d&#8217;information
            d&eacute;di&eacute;s : <i>productique, environnement, &eacute;ducation, sant&eacute;,
              commerce, banque&#8230;</i><o:p></o:p></span></li>
      </ul>
      <h1 style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span
          style="font-family:Times;mso-ansi-language:FR">Instructions
          aux auteurs :<o:p></o:p></span></h1>
      <h2 style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph">Types
        de contribution<o:p></o:p></h2>
      <p class="MsoNormal"
        style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span
          style="font-family:Times;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times
          New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New
          Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:FR">L&#8217;appel &agrave; communications
          sollicite des articles in&eacute;dits, non soumis &agrave; d&#8217;autres
          conf&eacute;rences ou journaux, de l&#8217;un des trois types suivants :<o:p></o:p></span></p>
      <ul>
        <li><span
            style="font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:


            Symbol;mso-ansi-language:FR"><span style="mso-list:Ignore"><span
                style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;"></span></span></span><b
            style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal"><span
              style="font-family:Times;mso-fareast-font-family:
              &quot;Times New
              Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New
              Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language: FR">Articles centr&eacute;s
              solutions</span></b><span style="font-family:Times;
            mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New
            Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New
            Roman&quot;; mso-ansi-language:FR"> : ces articles
            pr&eacute;sentent une probl&eacute;matique de recherche pour laquelle des
            solutions nouvelles ou des am&eacute;liorations significatives de
            solutions existantes sont d&eacute;velopp&eacute;es. Un article de ce type
            devrait inclure une validation pr&eacute;liminaire de la solution
            propos&eacute;e.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
        <li><span
            style="font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:


            Symbol;mso-ansi-language:FR"><span style="mso-list:Ignore"><span
                style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;"></span></span></span><b
            style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal"><span
              style="font-family:Times;mso-fareast-font-family:
              &quot;Times New
              Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New
              Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language: FR">Articles d&#8217;&eacute;valuation</span></b><span
            style="font-family:Times;mso-fareast-font-family:
            &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times
            New Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language: FR"> : ces articles
            &eacute;valuent des situations probl&eacute;matiques ou bien les solutions
            qui ont &eacute;t&eacute; propos&eacute;es au moyen de techniques scientifiques
            telles que les &eacute;tudes empiriques, les exp&eacute;riences, les
            &eacute;tudes de cas, les simulations etc.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
        <li><span
            style="font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:


            Symbol;mso-ansi-language:FR"><span style="mso-list:Ignore"><span
                style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;"></span></span></span><b
            style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal"><span
              style="font-family:Times;mso-fareast-font-family:
              &quot;Times New
              Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New
              Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language: FR">Articles d&#8217;exp&eacute;riences
              industrielles</span></b><span style="font-family:
            Times;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New
            Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New
            Roman&quot;; mso-ansi-language:FR"> : ces articles
            pr&eacute;sentent des probl&egrave;mes ou des d&eacute;fis rencontr&eacute;s en
            pratique, relatent des cas de succ&egrave;s ou d&#8217;&eacute;chec ou sont des
            rapports d&#8217;exp&eacute;rience de pratique industrielle.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
      </ul>
      <p class="MsoNormal"><span
          style="font-family:Times;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times
          New Roman&quot;;
          mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ansi-language:FR">Les
          soumissions sont faites dans l&#8217;une des cat&eacute;gories suivantes :
          <o:p></o:p></span></p>
      <ul>
        <li><span
            style="font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:


            Symbol;mso-ansi-language:FR"><span style="mso-list:Ignore"><span
                style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;"></span></span></span><span
            style="font-family:Times;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times
            New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:
            Arial;mso-ansi-language:FR">Chercheur, o&ugrave; les crit&egrave;res de
            s&eacute;lection sont l&#8217;originalit&eacute;, la qualit&eacute; et la maturit&eacute; de
            la proposition. Cette cat&eacute;gorie peut comporter la mention
            &#8216;industriel&#8217;. <o:p></o:p></span></li>
        <li><span
            style="font-size:12.5pt;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;


            mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;mso-ansi-language:FR"><span
              style="mso-list:Ignore"><span style="font:7.0pt
                &quot;Times New Roman&quot;"></span></span></span><span
            style="font-family: Times;">Jeune chercheur, pour les
            articles dont tous les co-auteurs sont des doctorants. <span
              style="mso-spacerun:yes">&nbsp;</span>Lors de la soumission,
            ces articles devront &ecirc;tre soumis en cochant la case "Jeunes
            chercheurs". Le prix du meilleur article "Jeunes chercheurs"
            pourra &ecirc;tre attribu&eacute; lors du congr&egrave;s.</span></li>
      </ul>
      <h2 style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph">Evaluation


        et publication<o:p></o:p></h2>
      <p class="MsoNormal"
        style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span
          style="font-family:Times;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times
          New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New
          Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:FR">Tous les articles seront
          &eacute;valu&eacute;s par trois lecteurs du comit&eacute; de programme. <o:p></o:p></span></p>
      <p class="MsoNormal"
        style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span
          style="font-family:Times;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times
          New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New
          Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:FR">Les articles s&eacute;lectionn&eacute;s
          seront publi&eacute;s dans les actes du congr&egrave;s et feront l&#8217;objet
          d&#8217;une pr&eacute;sentation orale lors du congr&egrave;s.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
      <p class="MsoNormal"
        style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span
          style="font-family:Times;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times
          New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New
          Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:FR">A l'issue du congr&egrave;s, les
          meilleurs articles seront s&eacute;lectionn&eacute;s pour un num&eacute;ro sp&eacute;cial
          soit de la revue &laquo;Ing&eacute;nierie des Syst&egrave;mes d&#8217;Information,
          Herm&egrave;s Lavoisier &raquo;, soit de la revue &laquo; Document Num&eacute;rique,
          Herm&egrave;s &#8211; Lavoisier &raquo;. <o:p></o:p></span></p>
      <p class="MsoNormal"
        style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span
          style="font-family:Times;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times
          New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New
          Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:FR">Les auteurs seront alors
          invit&eacute;s &agrave; r&eacute;diger une version &eacute;tendue de leur article pour la
          soumettre &agrave; un comit&eacute; de lecture sp&eacute;cifique.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
      <h2>Conditions de soumission<o:p></o:p></h2>
      <p class="MsoNormal"
        style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span
          style="font-family:Times;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times
          New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New
          Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:FR">Les articles sont limit&eacute;s &agrave;
          16 pages et devront se conformer au mod&egrave;le Hermes-Lavoisier
          disponible sur le site web du congr&egrave;s <a
            class="moz-txt-link-freetext"
            href="http://inforsid.fr/Biarritz2015/">http://inforsid.fr/Biarritz2015/</a>.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
      <p class="MsoNormal"
        style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span
          style="font-family:Times;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times
          New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New
          Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:FR">Les articles doivent
          comporter la mention d&#8217;un th&egrave;me majeur et &eacute;ventuellement d&#8217;un
          th&egrave;me mineur choisi parmi les th&eacute;matiques pr&eacute;d&eacute;finies ou les
          autres th&eacute;matiques. La langue officielle du congr&egrave;s est le
          fran&ccedil;ais. Toutefois le congr&egrave;s est ouvert aux contributions de
          langue anglaise. <o:p></o:p></span></p>
      <p class="MsoNormal"
        style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span
          style="font-family:Times;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times
          New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New
          Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:FR">Les articles doivent &ecirc;tre
          soumis en format PDF sur le site <o:p></o:p></span><span
          style="mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New
          Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;"
          lang="EN-GB"><span style="mso-field-code:&quot; HYPERLINK
            \0022https\:\/\/easychair\.org\/conferences\/?conf=inforsid2015\0022
            \\t \0022_blank\0022 &quot;"><span class="MsoHyperlink"><a
                class="moz-txt-link-freetext"
                href="https://easychair.org/conferences/?conf=inforsid2015">https://easychair.org/conferences/?conf=inforsid2015</a></span></span></span></p>
